kitty (reference implementation)
License: GPL-3.0
https://github.com/kovidgoyal/kitty

The font rendering pipeline in this project (src/font.rs, src/text.wgsl) was
independently implemented using kitty's source code as a reference for
technique and correctness. No kitty source code was copied. Specifically,
kitty's approach to FreeType hinting flag selection, glyph atlas construction,
monospace cell grid computation, and sRGB-aware contrast adjustment informed
our implementation.
